name: Funfetti
additionalNotes: This 5 x 50 stick comes crafted with aged Nicaraguan binder and filler tobaccos that sit inside an oily, a reddish-hue Sumatra wrapper. Sold in no frills craft paper bundles of 10, you can expect a solid medium to full-bodied smoke with tasty notes of spice, leather, earth, nutmeg, and a sweet creamy finish.
